title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your endless energy may lead you to believe you have plenty of money to burn now. However, even buying lots of low-cost items could start to add up quickly. You might convince yourself in the moment that you need them, but chances are you dont. Perhaps youre busying yourself with trivial things on impulse rather than consolidating your resources for a bigger undertaking you really want. Use more of what you already have to acquire what you want, not acquire more of what you wont use. Saving for tomorrow requires self-restraint today. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
